---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description =
  'Moving Cars 2026 Privacy Policy. Our commitment to protecting your personal information under the Australian Privacy Act and OAIC guidelines.';
const lastUpdated = '15 January 2026';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
      >
        <header class="mb-12 border-b border-slate-100 pb-8">
          <div
            class="text-amber-600 font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm"
          >
            Legal & Compliance
          </div>
          <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4"
          >
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
        </header>

        <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8 font-medium">
            Moving Cars is committed to protecting your privacy in your dealings
            with our organisation. This policy outlines how we handle personal
            information in accordance with the Australian Privacy Principles
            (APPs) and the Privacy Act 1988.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            1. Collection of Personal Information
          </h2>
          <p>
            We collect personal information that is reasonably necessary for our
            business functions. This includes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Identity Details</strong>: Name, address, phone number,
              and email address.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Service Details</strong>: Vehicle details (make/model),
              origin/destination addresses for transport, and booking history.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Digital Identifiers</strong>: IP address, device type, and
              usage data collected via cookies when you visit our website.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Financial Information</strong>: Payment transaction
              records (note: we do not store full credit card numbers; see
              Section 6).
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            2. Purpose of Collection
          </h2>
          <p>We collect and use your personal information primarily to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide requested vehicle transport services and quotes.</li>
            <li>Communicate with you regarding your bookings and updates.</li>
            <li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
            <li>Improve our website performance and user experience.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            3. Automated Decision-Making (Quoting)
          </h2>
          <p>
            Our website uses automated algorithms to provide instant car
            transport quotes. These decisions are based on data points such as
            distance, vehicle type, and current carrier availability. If you
            believe an automated quote is incorrect, you have the right to
            request a manual review by contacting our team.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            4. Disclosure & Overseas Data Flows
          </h2>
          <p>
            Moving Cars will not provide your personal information to third
            parties other than to facilitate the services you requested. This
            includes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Sub-contractors</strong>: Reliable transport carriers
              actually performing the vehicle move.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Overseas Disclosure</strong>: We use international service
              providers for technology hosting (Vercel - USA), payment
              processing (Square - USA/International), and analytics. We ensure
              these providers maintain standards equivalent to Australian
              privacy laws.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Law Enforcement</strong>: When required by Australian law
              or government agencies (e.g., ATO, WorkCover).
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            5. Security & Data Retention
          </h2>
          <p>
            We take all reasonable steps to protect your personal information
            from misuse, loss, and unauthorised access. This includes encryption
            (SSL/TLS) for data in transit and restricted internal access.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Retention:</strong> We retain your personal information only as
            long as necessary for the purpose it was collected or to comply with Australian
            tax and record-keeping laws (typically up to 7 years).
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            6. Credit Card Details
          </h2>
          <p>
            Any transactions using credit cards via our website are processed
            securely by <strong>Square</strong>. We do not store credit card
            details on our own servers.
          </p>
          <div
            class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-6 my-8 rounded-r-xl"
          >
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-0">
              Zero-Tolerance Policy: We do not under any circumstances sell,
              rent, or trade your email address or contact details to
              third-party marketers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            7. Your Rights (2026 Standards)
          </h2>
          <p>
            As part of our commitment to modern privacy standards, you have the
            following rights:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Access & Correction</strong>: You may request access to or
              correction of your data at any time.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Right to Erasure</strong>: You may request that we delete
              your personal data when it is no longer required for its original
              purpose.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Data Portability</strong>: You may request a
              machine-readable copy of the data you provided to us.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            8. Complaints and Contact
          </h2>
          <p>
            If you have an inquiry or complaint about how we handle your
            personal information, please write to us. We will respond within 30
            days.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you are not satisfied with our response, you may escalate your
            complaint to the <strong
              >Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC)</strong
            > at <a
              href="https://www.oaic.gov.au"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="text-amber-600 hover:underline">oaic.gov.au</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote CTA -->
        <div
          class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl mt-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8"
        >
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Safe & Compliant Transport</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">
              Your data is secure. Get a quote in seconds.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="https://ratecheck.movingcars.com.au/quote/v2"
            class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-900 font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105 inline-block text-center whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            Get Instant Quote
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
